SEMDL Help Topic: reference annotate

Usage:
- `ssd annotate <selector> <kind> <text> --target sidecar --dry-run <file>`

Purpose:
- Append rationale, caveat, todo, status, or explanation metadata.

Related help:
- `ssd help grammar`
- `ssd help samples`

Sample:
- `ssd annotate id:H1 rationale 原文に主語がないため補完 --target sidecar --dry-run docs/examples/minimal.ssd`
